        "full_width": true,
        "remove_vertical_spacing": true,
        "remove_horizontal_spacing": false,
        "liquid": "<!-- SECTION STATS -->\n<div style=\"padding: 40px 20px; background: #fff;\">\n  <div style=\"text-align: center; margin-bottom: 32px;\">\n    <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 8px 0;\">\n      Les Résultats <span style=\"color: #7c3aed;\">En Chiffres</span>\n    </h2>\n    <p style=\"font-size: 13px; color: #9ca3af; margin: 0;\">\n      Basé sur les retours clients et expériences auto-déclarées. Les résultats peuvent varier.\n    </p>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- STAT 1 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: #7c3aed; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 80px;\">96%</div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Sourire Visiblement Plus Blanc</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Les utilisatrices ont constaté des dents visiblement plus blanches dès les premiers jours, notamment sur les taches de café et les colorations du quotidien.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- STAT 2 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: #7c3aed; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 80px;\">94%</div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Zéro Élancement, Zéro Douleur</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Des femmes ayant déjà abandonné le blanchiment à cause de la sensibilité ont pu terminer la cure complète sans aucune douleur.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- STAT 3 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n    <div style=\"font-size: 48px; font-weight: 900; color: #7c3aed; line-height: 1; flex-shrink: 0; min-width: 80px;\">91%</div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Recommandent à leur Entourage</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Après leur première cure, la majorité des clientes ont recommandé NELORYA à une amie ou un proche ayant les mêmes problèmes de sensibilité.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>\n\n<!-- SECTION POURQUOI NELORYA -->\n<div style=\"padding: 40px 20px; background: #faf9ff;\">\n  <h2 style=\"font-size: 26px; font-weight: 800; color: #1a1a1a; margin: 0 0 32px 0;\">\n    Pourquoi NELORYA ?\n  </h2>\n\n  <!-- ITEM 1 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ede9fe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\">\n        <path d=\"M12 2C8 2 5 5 5 9c0 5 7 13 7 13s7-8 7-13c0-4-3-7-7-7z\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"9\" r=\"2.5\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Formule PAP Sans Peroxyde</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Notre technologie de 2ème génération blanchit sans peroxyde — le composé responsable de 100% des douleurs et élancements.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ITEM 2 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ede9fe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\">\n        <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <path d=\"M12 7v5l3 3\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">30 Minutes Seulement</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Appliquer, se détendre, retirer. Pas de gouttière, pas de lampe, pas d'étapes compliquées. Intégrable dans n'importe quelle routine.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ITEM 3 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 28px;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ede9fe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\">\n        <path d=\"M9 12l2 2 4-4\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n        <path d=\"M12 3l1.5 3 3.5.5-2.5 2.5.5 3.5L12 11l-3 1.5.5-3.5L7 6.5l3.5-.5L12 3z\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Résultats Visibles en 7 Jours</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Une cure complète de 7 jours pour jusqu'à 6 tons de différence. Des résultats mesurables sur le guide de teintes officiel.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- ITEM 4 -->\n  <div style=\"display: flex; align-items: flex-start; gap: 16px; margin-bottom: 0;\">\n    <div style=\"width: 52px; height: 52px; border-radius: 50%; background: #ede9fe; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; flex-shrink: 0;\">\n      <svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\">\n        <circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\"/>\n        <path d=\"M8 13s1.5 2 4 2 4-2 4-2\" stroke=\"#7c3aed\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke-linecap=\"round\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"9\" cy=\"10\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#7c3aed\"/>\n        <circle cx=\"15\" cy=\"10\" r=\"1\" fill=\"#7c3aed\"/>\n      </svg>\n    </div>\n    <div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 16px; font-weight: 700; color: #1a1a1a; margin-bottom: 4px;\">Confiance Retrouvée</div>\n      <div style=\"font-size: 14px; color: #6b7280; line-height: 1.6;\">Des milliers de femmes ont retrouvé l'envie de sourire sur les photos. Sans douleur, sans compromis, sans se priver.</div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n</div>",
